data.description: Charming Bi-Level Home in Penn Hills School District with 3-bedroom, 3-bath, 2-car garage  providing convenient parking and ample storage space.   One of the highlights of this property is the finished basement, adding valuable additional living space. Whether you desire a recreation room, home office, or a cozy movie night setting, the basement can accommodate all your needs.  For comfort in all seasons, the home features gas heating and central air conditioning, ensuring your year-round climate control. This means you'll stay cozy during the winter months and enjoy cool, refreshing air in the summer.    Outside, the property offers a lovely backyard space where you can relax, entertain, and create your own outdoor place.   Don't miss the opportunity to make this charming 3-bedroom bi-level home your own. Schedule a viewing today and discover the possibilities and comfort this property has to offer.
